// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1249 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bb94f6ad-b787-5a2c-b284-2f7874fcbea3

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:19.04*")
